      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed. GCI for hemolysis index on fine mesh (33.6M cells) is 4.2%, meeting the 5% threshold. Asymptotic convergence ratio p=1.97 confirms solution is in the convergent regime. Gradation 3 achieved."
