      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same geometry used in the COU. Operating conditions span the full range of COU flow-speed combinations. Blood analogue fluid properties match COU conditions within documented bounds. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
