      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis sub-model selections justified with reference to published literature for similar blood pump applications.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark comparisons for intravascular pump flows. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model selected as the regulatory standard for comparative hemolysis assessment. Model form assumptions documented and justified. Gradation 1 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
