      "rationale": "Formal sensitivity analysis of model input parameters (e.g., blood viscosity, pump geometry tolerances) to output hemolysis index not conducted. At MRL 2 with the current resource constraints, this factor is deferred. Inlet velocity profile uncertainty estimated qualitatively as low based on fully-developed flow assumption at 10D upstream. Not assessed per MRL 2 scoping decision."
